HEADER  PARITWOO linkule test — parity-dependent WS depth
$ Tests the PARITWOO potential-form linkule. Depth scaled by (1 + PARAM1*(-1)^L).
CHANNEL  3He + 4He
ELAB = 30
PARAMETERSET EL2  ASYMPTOPIA=20
realpotential PARITWOO
V = 80  R = 1.6  A = 0.7  REALPOWE = 1.0  PARAM1 = -0.2  RC0 = 1.3
W = 10  RI0 = 1.6  AI = 0.7
ELASTIC SCATTERING
;
end
